#
# Description: Script for mydiag diagnostic pack setting
#              
#
# Input:  - mydiag_dom_freq.ini ini file (MUST be stored in the same directory of mydiag_dom_freq_selection.sh script) 
#         - templates contained in the "templates/" directory (MUST be stored in the same directory of mydiag_dom_freq_selection.sh script) 
#         - the exp src directory on which you want to apply the changes (linked in the ini file)
#
# Output: mydiag scripts with the specific settings for the choosen case, namely
#         - mydiag.sh, gen_xml.sh, exp_mrsp.sh, exp_filter_reduce.sh, exp_filter_map.sh in %exp%/pack/med_prod/bin directory
#         - diag_base_eas3.TEMPLATE.xml in %exp%/pack/med_prod directory
#         - a copy of the previous versions of the script (named *_old ) in the same directories
# 
# Initialization file (required): mydiag_dom_freq.ini 
#
# WARNING: This script is going to modify the src of mydiag package..
#
# How to run the script:
#
#  1) Set variable values in the initialization file (mydiag_dom_freq.ini) 
#     Reading CAREFULLY the WARNINGS in the file before running the script...
#
#  2) Run the shell script:  sh mydiag_dom_freq_selection.sh
#
# Good luck
#
#
#         
